data.title: Ringo Starr
data.meta_description: Musician and songwriter. Born Liverpool. One of the four Beatles, the drummer in the group, though, when asked whether Ringo was the best drummer in the world, John Lennon replied: 'He's not even the best drummer in The Beatles'. Cruel, John, cruel.
